# BrandSync Collective DAO
A decentralized autonomous organization (DAO) smart contract built on the Stacks blockchain for managing brand collaborations, influencer partnerships, and community-driven marketing campaigns with transparent voting, reputation management, and automated fund distribution.

## Table of Contents
- [Overview](#overview)
- [Features](#features)
- [Contract Architecture](#contract-architecture)
- [Getting Started](#getting-started)
- [Core Functions](#core-functions)
- [Governance Parameters](#governance-parameters)
- [Error Codes](#error-codes)
- [Usage Examples](#usage-examples)
- [Security Considerations](#security-considerations)

## Overview

BrandSync Collective DAO enables communities to democratically vote on brand collaboration proposals, manage treasury funds, and track partnership performance. Members can submit proposals, vote on collaborations, and earn reputation points for successful contributions.

## Features
###  **Democratic Governance**
- Transparent voting system with quorum requirements
- Reputation-based member scoring
- Customizable voting periods (24 hours to 1 week)

###  **Treasury Management**
- Collective fund pooling and distribution
- Automated fund allocation for approved proposals
- Balance tracking and validation

###  **Brand Analytics**
- Partnership performance tracking
- Success metrics and funding history
- Brand blacklisting capabilities

###  **Membership System**
- Open membership registration
- Voluntary exit mechanism
- Reputation scoring system

## Contract Architecture
### Data Structures

- **`dao-member-profiles`**: Member information and voting credentials
- **`collaboration-proposals`**: Brand partnership proposals with voting data
- **`member-proposal-votes`**: Individual vote tracking
- **`brand-collaboration-analytics`**: Brand performance metrics

### Key Constants
- **Minimum Voting Period**: 144 blocks (~24 hours)
- **Maximum Voting Period**: 1,008 blocks (~1 week)
- **Required Quorum**: 30% member participation
- **Approval Threshold**: 51% majority
- **Initial Reputation**: 100 points per member

## Getting Started
### Prerequisites
- Stacks blockchain environment
- Clarity smart contract deployment tools
- STX tokens for transaction fees

### Deployment
1. Deploy the contract to the Stacks blockchain
2. The deployer automatically becomes the contract owner
3. Initial treasury balance starts at 0

### Joining the DAO
```clarity
(contract-call? .brandsync-dao join-brandsync-collective)
```

## Core Functions
### Membership Management
#### Join the DAO
```clarity
(define-public (join-brandsync-collective))
```
- Allows new users to become DAO members
- Assigns initial reputation score of 100 points
- Grants voting weight of 1

#### Exit the DAO
```clarity
(define-public (exit-brandsync-collective))
```
- Voluntary membership termination
- Deactivates member profile
- Reduces active member count

### Proposal Management
#### Submit Collaboration Proposal
```clarity
(define-public (submit-collaboration-proposal 
    (collaboration-title (string-ascii 100))
    (detailed-description (string-ascii 500))
    (target-brand-name (string-ascii 50))
    (requested-funding-amount uint)
    (partnership-category (string-ascii 30))
    (voting-duration-blocks uint)))
```

**Parameters:**
- `collaboration-title`: Brief proposal title (max 100 characters)
- `detailed-description`: Comprehensive description (max 500 characters)
- `target-brand-name`: Brand partner name (max 50 characters)
- `requested-funding-amount`: Funding request in STX
- `partnership-category`: Collaboration type (max 30 characters)
- `voting-duration-blocks`: Voting period (144-1008 blocks)

#### Cast Vote
```clarity
(define-public (cast-collaboration-vote (collaboration-proposal-id uint) (approve-proposal bool)))
```
- Vote on active proposals
- One vote per member per proposal
- Must vote before voting period ends

#### Execute Approved Proposal
```clarity
(define-public (execute-approved-collaboration (collaboration-proposal-id uint)))
```
- Processes completed votes
- Distributes funds if approved
- Updates reputation scores

### Treasury Management
#### Contribute Funds
```clarity
(define-public (contribute-to-collective-treasury (contribution-amount uint)))
```
- Add funds to collective treasury
- Increases available funding pool

### Query Functions
#### Get Proposal Details
```clarity
(define-read-only (get-collaboration-proposal-details (collaboration-proposal-id uint)))
```
#### Get Member Profile
```clarity
(define-read-only (get-dao-member-profile (member-address principal)))
```
#### Get Treasury Balance
```clarity
(define-read-only (get-collective-treasury-balance))
```
## Governance Parameters
| Parameter | Value | Description |
|-----------|--------|-------------|
| Minimum Voting Period | 144 blocks | ~24 hours |
| Maximum Voting Period | 1,008 blocks | ~1 week |
| Quorum Requirement | 30% | Minimum participation |
| Approval Threshold | 51% | Required majority |
| Initial Reputation | 100 points | New member score |
| Success Bonus | 10 points | Reward for approved proposals |

## Error Codes
| Code | Constant | Description |
|------|----------|-------------|
| u100 | ERR-UNAUTHORIZED-ACCESS | Insufficient permissions |
| u101 | ERR-COLLABORATION-PROPOSAL-NOT-FOUND | Invalid proposal ID |
| u102 | ERR-MEMBER-ALREADY-CAST-VOTE | Duplicate voting attempt |
| u103 | ERR-VOTING-PERIOD-HAS-ENDED | Vote submitted too late |
| u104 | ERR-VOTING-STILL-IN-PROGRESS | Execution attempted early |
| u105 | ERR-TREASURY-INSUFFICIENT-BALANCE | Insufficient funds |
| u106 | ERR-INVALID-FUNDING-AMOUNT | Invalid funding request |
| u107 | ERR-USER-NOT-DAO-MEMBER | Non-member action attempt |
| u108 | ERR-USER-ALREADY-DAO-MEMBER | Duplicate membership |
| u109 | ERR-COLLABORATION-PROPOSAL-REJECTED | Proposal failed vote |
| u110 | ERR-INVALID-VOTING-DURATION | Invalid voting period |
| u111 | ERR-INVALID-STRING-INPUT | Invalid text input |

## Usage Examples
### Creating a Brand Partnership Proposal

```clarity
;; Submit a proposal for Nike collaboration
(contract-call? .brandsync-dao submit-collaboration-proposal
    "Nike Sneaker Launch Campaign"
    "Promote new Air Max release through social media and influencer partnerships targeting Gen Z demographics with focus on sustainability messaging"
    "Nike"
    u5000000 ;; 50 STX
    "Fashion & Lifestyle"
    u288) ;; 48 hours voting period
```
### Voting on a Proposal
```clarity
;; Vote to approve proposal #1
(contract-call? .brandsync-dao cast-collaboration-vote u1 true)

;; Vote to reject proposal #2
(contract-call? .brandsync-dao cast-collaboration-vote u2 false)
```
### Checking Proposal Status
```clarity
;; Get details for proposal #1
(contract-call? .brandsync-dao get-collaboration-proposal-details u1)

;; Check if member has voted
(contract-call? .brandsync-dao check-member-voting-status u1 'SP1ABCD...)
```

## Security Considerations
### Access Control
- Contract owner has emergency administrative powers
- Members can only vote on proposals once
- Only active members can participate in governance

### Validation
- Comprehensive input validation for all text fields
- Funding amount validation
- Voting period constraints
- Treasury balance verification

### Reputation System
- Prevents gaming through transparent scoring
- Rewards successful proposal creators
- Tracks member contributions over time

## Administrative Functions
### Brand Blacklisting
```clarity
(define-public (blacklist-brand-partner (target-brand-name (string-ascii 50))))
```
- **Owner only**: Add brands to blacklist for policy violations

### Emergency Member Removal
```clarity
(define-public (remove-dao-member-emergency (target-member-address principal)))
```
- **Owner only**: Remove members in emergency situations
## Proposal Lifecycle
1. **Submission**: Member submits collaboration proposal
2. **Voting**: Active members cast votes during voting period
3. **Evaluation**: System checks quorum and majority requirements
4. **Execution**: Approved proposals trigger fund distribution
5. **Analytics**: Brand metrics and member reputation updated